page.title: 02A Walk round Chobham
page.content:
On our walk we stopped off at the Chobham{Post Office}and a{postman}was going right across it on his{bicycle and Mrs Eccles took a picture of him, also this is an amenity.
We{walked}for a long way and we came to Chobham Common and photographed the{motorway,}which goes right across the common.{Chobham Common}is a stretch of land which is used for leisure.
We came to some{nurseries}near {Jubilee Mount}which we took pictures of. We found a{Bus stop}and we took a picture of it because it is a{bus {route.}
I took some pictures of people and other{shops.
